title: 39 Christmas Music Videos - Xvid - Slimoo
description:
39 Christmas Music Videos - Xvid - Slimoo

OK what this is

I recorded about 10 hours of those Christmas Video Shows
You know the type, 40 biggest Xmas hits, 20 biggest Xmas hits

I then chopped them up to remove adverts and the Host

I then took the 39 vids and created this 2 hour 20 minute video

All the classics and some that where there because there was some snow in the video

Elton John, Slade, Wizard, Cliff, Hall And Oats, Wham, The Pogues, S Club 7, Westlife
Bing, McCartney, Greg Lake, Band Aid



As this is likely only played for a week or 2 I never put to much effort into the edits
Just simple fades


Seed until Christmas so everyone gets a decent speed
